title: Stardom Goddesses of Stardom Tag League 2025 - Day 4
overview: The fourth night of Stardom Goddesses of Stardom Tag League 2025 took place on November 12, 2025, at Sendai PIT in Sendai, Miyagi, Japan, and was headlined by a Block A match between STARS (Bea Priestley & Saya Iida) and God's Eye (Ami Sourei & Lady C).
